de.griefed.serverpackcreatoraddonexample.configuration

Class ConfigurationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.griefed.serverpackcreatoraddonexample.configuration.ConfigurationModel

  • public class ConfigurationModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The model for the configuration which is passed to us by ServerPackCreator. It is filled by ConfigurationHandler during the beginning of Main and from then on available for use.
